Package org.autogui.base.type

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    GuiTypeElement
    the super-type for describing information of a type, a property, or an action.
    GuiUpdatedValue
    a value wrapper for changed property values:
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GuiTypeBuilder
    the factory for GuiTypeElement.
    GuiTypeBuilder.GuiTypeBuilderRelaxed
    another type-builder with relaxed rules: including non-public (without access-modifiers) members.
    GuiTypeBuilder.MemberDefinitions
    a temporarily created member group in GuiTypeBuilder.createObjectFromClass(Class,Type)
    GuiTypeBuilder.MemberDefinitionsForNotifier  
    GuiTypeCollection
    a type information about Collection<E> .
    GuiTypeCollectionArray
    type information about an array.
    GuiTypeMember
    the super type for actions and properties
    GuiTypeMember.MemberOrdinal
    an ordinal information of a member
    GuiTypeMemberAction
    a type information for public R m() { ...
    GuiTypeMemberActionList
    an action taking a list: processing the selected items in a table public R m(List<E> selectedItems) { ...
    GuiTypeMemberProperty
    a type information about a property.
    GuiTypeMemberPropertyNotifier
    a type information about setter of notifier: basically, it is intended to have only a setter with the GuiNotifierSetter annotation
    GuiTypeObject
    an object type, which has actions and properties.
    GuiTypeValue
    primitive types, their associated boxed types, String, ...
    GuiUpdatedValue.GuiUpdatedValueNone
    the no value for GuiUpdatedValue, can be obtained by GuiUpdatedValue.NO_UPDATE
    GuiUpdatedValue.GuiUpdatedValueObject
    the value holder for GuiUpdatedValue
